description: Hot pleated short dress just for you! Purple and white print wraps around the entire dress with short sleeves and scoop neck. Looks fab with cute ballet flats.

name: White Black V-Cut Sheer Dress
description: Look cute and sexy at the same time! White and black dress with a plunging v-neck line with sheer. Zipper in the back with more peek-a-boo sheer. Wear with black booties or pumps for a fun night out!

name: Walk this Way Legging

description: Want to spice up your wardrobe? These sexy black leggings cut off from the thigh high down to above the knee for a peek-a-boo look with see through mesh. Wear under a dress with sassy heels.

name: Love Lace blouse
description: Its all about the love. And we love this unique see through black top. It comes with lace on the shoulders and a love button at the collar. Long sleeve and button down. Looks fresh with black shorts or skinny jeans.

description: Shiny metallic gold detailing all around the jacket. Cut to the waist and stylishly paired with white pants.

name: Olive Sequins Jacket

name: Sheer leg Stirups leggings
description: Add some edge to your outfit with these see through leggings. Thick line down the center of each leg for some extra style makes these leggings classic yet modern. Pair with a long t-shirt or wear them under a cute dress.

name: Denim Stud
description: Instead of borrowing your boyfriends button ups, have your own! The perfect button for any outfit. Light denim with shoulder and back gold studs. Long sleeved with two front pockets. Wear with jeans or over a dress.

name: Hail a Taxie in my Maxie
description: Hot maxi dress in purple. Includes v-neck line, long sleeves and a sexy slit. Looks great alone or with a chunky belt and black booties.

description: Amazing ethnic prints in the front and see through back. Oversized fit. Awesomely paired with olive pants and black flat booties.

name: Abstract Cardigan
description: Cute oversized cardi with blue and brown detailing. Ribbed detailing and button down. Looks great with a simple look or over a dress.

name: American Skull T-Shirt
description: Super comfy T-shirt with a true American skull in the front. Pair it with jeans or comfy pants to complete the look.

name: Snake Skin Moto Jacket
description: Faux snake skin jacket featuring faux leather sleeves with a zipper at the chest. Looks great with our black sheer heart cutout blouse.

name: Shirt Dress
description: Is it a shirt? Is it a dress? Just depends on how you want to wear it! Beautiful fuschia colored shirt dress with long sleeves and buttoned down. Intricate lace detailing on the back. Pair it with leggings, jeans, or tights...its up to you!

name: Winter white leggings
description: Don't be stuck wearing all black this season! White is in and these are super hot! Pocket lines on each side with uneven zipper patterns on each knee to make it unique. Wear it with a long shirt and flats or heels for some extra attitude! Also available in black.

name: G.I Jane Camo Dress
description: This camouflage doesn't blend in with everyone else but makes you stand out! Cream, dark brown and blue colors all around with buttons to the waist. Longer in the back length with cut off shoulders and a collar. Looks awesome with brown or blue flats.

name: Army Jacket
description: Super cute army jacket for all seasons. Wear it with a plain white T-shirt and jeans.

description: Button down sheer top for any occasion. Styling heart details on the back for an even cooler look. Paired with red pants and brown booties.
